Introduction
---

**[ABC]** is a startup e-commerce platform that wants to run its applications on AWS. The application is based on microservices, with the backend separated from the frontend.

---
### Requirements:

1. We lack sufficient cloud expertise.
2. We want to deploy our POC as quickly as possible.
3. We want to set request limits to our endpoints.
4. We need a good secure environment because we build and manage our own payment systems.
5. We want to restrict users in Ghana from deleting items.
6. We want to prevent Cross-Site Scripting (XSS).
8. We want to secure all backend services with API keys.